Harry Schumm https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Schumm 0 Harry Schumm (September 27, 1877 – April 4, 1953) was an American film actor of the silent era. He appeared in almost 50 films between 1913 and 1920. He was born in Chicago, Illinois and died in Los Angeles, California.
